testem.json is the config file
can use jasmin or other frameworks
src files can be *nix glob patterns

testem.json
{
  "launch": "phantomjs"
  "framework": "jasmine"
  "src_files": [
    "src/**/*.js",
    "spec/**/*.js"
  ]
}

spec/
src/


# can use xunit ci mode 
# or run in continuous mode and watch for file changes in src/ or /test
testem ci -R xunit
# or testem ci -R dot, testem -ci > (send to file for jenkins)


